description: For sale: $825,000. Beautiful, custom-built walkout rambler with over 1.2 million invested. Situated on 2.7 acres high on a hill with incredible views spanning to the Mississippi River and Cannon River Valley. Under 10 minutes to Mayo Health Center and everyday shops. Less than a mile to the Cannon Valley Trail and quick access to 61. This expansive home features oversized windows with a large open plan. Enjoy all the conveniences of 1-level living along with the luxury of a large observation room with sweeping views upstairs and fully finished walkout lower level - both accessible from the full-size elevator. The main floor has it all with a large, open living, dining, and kitchen with center island, and a large master suite including a soaking tub and steam shower. A large theater and sauna are in the walk-out lower level. Built with energy efficiency in mind: spray-foam insulation throughout and 9 zones of in-floor heating. So many features in this custom home - best to see them all in person.
